platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: Deciphering this game is no easy taskit feels like a metaphor. Is it a commentary on the fragile nature of trust and human connection? A scathing critique of our blind adherence to authority? Or is it just really weird? Regardless, INSIDE is an incredible journey with increasingly bizarre encounters that mix action with clever puzzle designs. The game isnt meant to be entirely understood. Its meant to be experienced.
